parameters: Search for yourself on social media

Memimi: Thanks to the increase in our organization's
members, we've been able to add more staff to Zigzag Mart.
We can't let our guard down here; we must take our
customers' opinions seriously and further solidify our
management...

Memimi: ...A response already... It's good that it came, but
this, this comment is troubling...

Memimi: The Anomalocaris keychain is quietly becoming a
trend in the city, especially among women... It brings back
memories, so I don't really want to see it...

Memimi: Uh, uh-huh... It's not really... useful as a
reference, is it...

Memimi: ...I knew something like this would come... Damn
it... the photo... ugh...

Memimi: The match with Mayor Orca is just around the
corner... To know my enemy, I should do a little research on
him...

Memimi: Ah, there it is... Oh, he's getting bashed... That
guy is seriously hated, huh...

Memimi: ...Well, I'm probably in the same boat... Ahh, this
is so demotivating... Ugh... don't post pictures like
that... unedited, with my face showing...

Memimi: The great boss has gifted me a DVD... It's a cool
shark movie for reference for my techniques... It's a
masterpiece among masterpieces, featuring sharks flying in a
typhoon, and it's even been made into a series...

Memimi: With this, the likes of Mayor Orca will be nothing
to worry about!! I'll develop an overwhelmingly new
technique and delight the great boss!!
